content: Set up a Twitter account for Xander. It's time to start testing how it interacts with the world. The responses are rudimentary, but it's a start. Here we go, @XanderAI.
Xander's first tweet went out today. The feedback is mixed, but I'm learning what resonates with people. It's a bit like putting a child in the world, watching it navigate.
Reflecting on the last two months since I returned to NYC. Xander has gone from an idea to a project with real-world interaction. There's still so much to learn, but I'm on my way.
